organic.title: UC Davis Comprehensive Cancer Center
organic.snippet: UC Davis Comprehensive Cancer Center is among only 57 cancer centers in the United States designated as a “comprehensive” cancer center.

organic.title: UC Davis Cancer Care Network
organic.snippet: The UC Davis Cancer Care Network provides leadership in transformative cancer care, research, and education for diverse communities in California.

organic.title: Comparative Cancer Center - UC Davis
organic.snippet: Comparative Cancer Center specializing in the diagnosis, treatment, and clinical care of animals with cancer.

organic.title: UC Davis Comprehensive Cancer Center
organic.snippet: It is the only NCI-Designated Cancer Center located in the Central Valley of Northern California and thus is best positioned to address the cancer burden.
